<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM5.5.9">
<l>muṉṉiṉ ṟāyeṉṟu tōḻimārkaḷu maṉṉaiya rumuṉitir</l>
<l>maṉṉu māṭat tirukkuṟuṅkuṭi nampiyai nāṉkaṇṭapiṉ</l>
<l>ceṉṉi nīṇmuṭi yātiyāya vulappi laṇikalattaṉ</l>
<l>kaṉṉal pālamu tākivanteṉ ṉeñcaṅ kaḻiyāṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>“You stood in front”, so you disapprove, friends and mothers.</l>
<l>After I saw Nampi of Tirukkuṟuṅkuṭi with permanent storied mansions,</l>
<l>he with flawless adorning ornaments that begin with the long crown on top,</l>
<l>came as milk [and] ambrosia in a pot(?) [and] does not slip from my heart.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
